## Summary
This documentation explains how Amplitude tracks and processes location, IP address, user agent, and device properties. It details how MaxMind database is used for geolocation, how location data is preserved even when IP addresses are blocked, and how user agent strings are parsed to extract device information like model, OS, browser, and platform for analytics purposes.

